<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Jdk on 编程心语</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/tags/jdk/</link><description>Recent content in Jdk on 编程心语</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 15 Apr 2021 19:47:30 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ithome.me/tags/jdk/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>怎样在Centos中安装Oracle JDK</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2021/04/15/%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E5%9C%A8centos%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85oracle-jdk/</link><pubDate>Thu, 15 Apr 2021 19:47:30 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2021/04/15/%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E5%9C%A8centos%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85oracle-jdk/</guid><description>&lt;h4 id="解决方案"&gt;解决方案&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;从&lt;a href="https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/javase/javase-jdk8-downloads.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;这里&lt;/a&gt;
下载最新的JDK. 现在CentOs (Linux x64 RPM Package) , &lt;a href="https://download.oracle.com/otn/java/jdk/8u281-b09/89d678f2be164786b292527658ca1605/jdk-8u281-linux-x64.rpm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;jdk-8u281-linux-x64.rpm&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;chmod +x jdk-8u281-linux-x64.rpm&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;yum install jdk-8u281-linux-x64.rpm&lt;/code&gt; &lt;code&gt;Java&lt;/code&gt;会被安装在&lt;code&gt;/usr/java&lt;/code&gt;目录&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;alternatives --config java&lt;/code&gt; 选择你要的Java版本&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;验证你的Java版本&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;java version &amp;#34;1.8.0_281&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build 1.8.0_281-b09)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (build 25.281-b09, mixed mode)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
